headline: UnitedHealth doctors helped it collect billions from Medicare, WSJ says
summary: Doctors who work for UnitedHealth (UNH) are given a checklist of potential diagnoses before they examine Medicare Advantage patients, Christopher Weaver, Anna Wilde Mathews and Tom McGinty of Wall Street Journal report.
